{
  "texts": [
    "A researcher was always present to assist the moderator (e.g.",
    "if a research question came up that the moderator was not sure how to answer) but was not visible on the participants' screens.",
    "The participants discussed each of the samples reviewed in pre-work, and at the close of the deliberation for each sample, again provided a rating of the sample (anonymous to other participants) with the same 7-point Likert scale as in the pre-work questionnaire.",
    "At the close of the focus group, time was reserved for a \"cool down\" conversation to reflect on the process and discussion.",
    "The moderator ensured that every participant had the opportunity to provide their feedback on the process, either in-session or through a follow-up survey."
  ]
}